      </div>
      <div>
        <h5 class="text-base font-medium font-heading text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-100 tracking-tight">Product updates</h5>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Read about upcoming changes.</p>
